{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Menurut Survei, Inilah 8 Jenis Gamer Masa Kini","content":"\n<p>Jenis gamer seperti apakah kamu? Apakah kamu seorang gamer kasual yang senang bermain game di smartphone? Atau kamu adalah gamer hardcore yang mengoleksi semua jenis konsol dan gamenya?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Saat berbicara tentang sosok dan kepribadian seorang gamer, topik kasual dan hardcore biasanya jadi bahan omongan yang hangat. Ada alasan kenapa seseorang bisa dianggap gamer kasual atau hardcore. Bisa jadi dia bermain game agar tidak bosan di busway atau kereta. Bisa jadi dia seorang atlit esport. Bisa jadi dia seorang Youtuber. Tapi ternyata, konsep gamer kasual dan hardcore sekarang sudah dianggap usang, setidaknya menurut survei/penelitian yang dilakukan oleh Newzoo.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lwijYwA22mA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<h2>Perkembangan esports jadi salah satu faktor lahirnya jenis gamer baru.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Perusahaan analisis Newzoo menyatakan bahwa selama 15 tahun terakhir, perkembangan teknologi dan video game telah menjadikan jargon gamer kasual dan hardcore kedaluarsa. Dengan merebaknya teknologi internet dan streaming, serta merebaknya kebudayaan baru dari teknologi tersebut seperti live streaming dan esport, semakin menambah kompleks vektor atau variabel untuk menentukan apakah seseorang merupakan gamer kasual atau hardcore.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk mengatasi “masalah tersebut”, Newzoo meneliti selama\nsatu tahun terakhir seperti apa sih cara menentukan jenis gamer masa kini?\nDengan memperhitungkan faktor-faktor perkembangan di atas, mereka menentukan\ntiga elemen penting untuk menentukan seperti apa jenis gamer masa kini: Playing\n(seberapa sering seseorang bermain game), Watching (seberapa sering seseorang\nmenonton orang lain bermain game), dan Owning (seberapa banyak seseorang\nmembeli game).</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53982\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/01-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Hasil penelitian Newzoo terhadap jenis gamer masa kini. Sumber: Newzoo\" class=\"wp-image-53982\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Hasil penelitian Newzoo terhadap jenis gamer masa kini. Sumber: Newzoo</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Berdasarkan hasil penelitian dan wawancara dengan sejumlah\ngamer, Newzoo berhasil menemukan delapan jenis gamer masa kini yang mewakili\nkebiasaan dan intensitas hobi game mereka. Penasaran seperti apa jenis gamer\ntersebut? Simak di bawah ini, diurutkan dari jumlah yang paling banyak!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Delapan Jenis Gamer Masa Kini</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Time Filler (27%) – Main Game Untuk Mengisi Waktu Luang</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53983\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/02-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Macet? Santai, main game aja dulu. Sumber: Travel Assistant India\" class=\"wp-image-53983\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Macet? Santai, main game aja dulu. Sumber: Travel Assistant India</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Jenis gamer dalam kategori Time Filler adalah gamer yang\nbisa dikatakan kasual di masa lalu. Maksudnya adalah para gamer dalam kategori\nini mengisi waktu kosong mereka dengan bermain game. Entah itu untuk menunggu\ngiliran saat mengantri atau saat duduk di dalam perjalanan panjang. Mereka\nhanya menganggap game permainan sederhana seperti Tetris atau Candy Crush.\nSingkat, mudah dimainkan, dan tidak butuh investasi waktu panjang.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Cloud Gamer (19%) – Gamer Pecinta Steam</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53984\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/03-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Berapa total koleksi game kamu di Steam? Sumber: Polygon\" class=\"wp-image-53984\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Berapa total koleksi game kamu di Steam? Sumber: Polygon</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam jenis gamer Cloud Gamer, gamer jenis ini adalah mereka\nyang setia menggunakan platform gaming seperti Steam, PS Store, Xbox Live,\nOrigin, Uplay, Epic Games Store, dan lain sebagainya. Gamer jenis ini membeli\ngame mereka melalui layanan online di atas. Mereka juga mengincar judul-judul\ngame free-to-play dan diskonan. Para Cloud Gamer sangat jarang membeli konsol/hardware\nbaru, dan hanya melakukan upgrade jika dibutuhkan saja.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Popcorn Gamer (13%) – Hobi Nonton Esports</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53985\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/04-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Menonton pertandingan esports kini bisa secara langsung di lokasinya. Sumber: Blizzard\" class=\"wp-image-53985\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Menonton pertandingan esports kini bisa secara langsung di lokasinya. Sumber: Blizzard</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Popcorn Gamer seperti pecinta olahraga. Jenis gamer yang satu ini bisa dikatakan bisa bermain game; bisa jago bisa nggak; tapi intensitas bermain mereka kalah jauh dibanding hobi mereka menonton orang lain bermain game. Entah itu menonton live streaming di Youtube atau Twitch, atau menyaksikan kompetisi esports favorit. Mereka suka game, belum tentu sering bermain, tapi pastinya menyukai ketegangan dan drama dari permainan orang lain.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/onic-esports-menangkan-mobile-legends-professional-league-indonesia-season-3/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ONIC Esports Menangkan Mobile Legends Professional League Indonesia</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. Ultimate Gamer (13%) – Hardcore Gamer Masa Kini</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53986\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/05-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Lihat koleksi gamenya! Sumber: Overly Positive\" class=\"wp-image-53986\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Lihat koleksi gamenya! Sumber: Overly Positive</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultimate gamer tidak berbeda dengan para hardcore gamer di\nmasa lalu. Mereka menghabiskan uang dan waktu mereka untuk bermain dan membeli\ngame. Saking berdedikasinya, mereka tidak punya waktu untuk menonton live\nstream atau apapun itu. Yang ada di kepala mereka adalah main game dan beli\ngame. &nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. All-Around Enthusiast (9%) – Gamer Sehat dan Sempurna</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53987\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/06-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Tahu kapan waktunya main dan kapan waktunya nonton. Sumber: Famous People\" class=\"wp-image-53987\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/06-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Tahu kapan waktunya main dan kapan waktunya nonton. Sumber: Famous People</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>All-Around Enthusiast merupakan jenis gamer yang tertarik\ndengan segala aktivitas bertema video game. Mereka senang bermain game, suka membeli\ngame, dan senang menonton orang lain bermain game. Jika meminjam kata-kata\nThanos, All-Around Enthusiast adalah gamer yang seimbang dan seharusnya\ndemikian.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. Hardware Enthusiast (6%) – Up to Date Dengan Teknologi</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53988\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/07-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Saking banyaknya, koleksinya bisa dijadikan museum. Sumber: PCMag\" class=\"wp-image-53988\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/07-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Saking banyaknya, koleksinya bisa dijadikan museum. Sumber: PCMag</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Jenis gamer Hardware Enthusiast bisa dikatakan sultan-nya para gamer. Buat mereka, membeli konsol game baru di tanggal rilisnya adalah sebuah kewajiban. Mereka ingin menjadi orang pertama yang menjajal teknologi baru dalam dunia game. Mereka adalah orang yang sudah mengantri dari subuh untuk membeli PS4 Pro dengan teknologi 4K dan HDR. Mereka adalah orang yang inden pertama kali untuk membeli video card Nvidia RTX 2080 Ti demi menjajal teknologi ray tracing terbaru di komputer mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gosip-panas-playstation-5-paling-cepat-muncul-di-2020/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gosip&nbsp;Panas&nbsp;PS5: Paling&nbsp;Cepat&nbsp;Muncul&nbsp;2020</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>7. Backseat Viewer (6%) – Mantan Gamer Nggak Bisa Move On</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53989\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/08-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Mengenang masa-masa main game seperti mengenang masa-masa bersama si dia. Sumber: ClickOnDetroit\" class=\"wp-image-53989\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/08-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Mengenang masa-masa main game seperti mengenang masa-masa bersama si dia. Sumber: ClickOnDetroit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Jenis gamer yang satu ini dulunya merupakan seorang gamer,\nentah itu kasual atau hardcore. Namun kesibukan kerja atau kuliah memaksa\nmereka untuk meninggalkan kegiatan main game untuk waktu yang lama. Mereka\ntidak bermain game lagi karena memang sudah sibuk atau tidak punya semangat\nlagi. Namun dalam beberapa kesempatan mereka menyempatkan diri menonton orang\nmain game untuk merasakan kembali passion saat mereka bermain game. Terjebak\nnostalgia, kalau kata Raisa.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>8. Conventional Gamer (4%) – Ras Langka di Era Modern</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53990\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menurut-survei-inilah-8-jenis-gamer-masa-kini/attachment/09-8-jenis-gamer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-8-jenis-gamer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer.jpg\" alt=\"Main game sekarang nggak cuma sekedar main aja. Sumber: Video Game History\" class=\"wp-image-53990\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/09-8-jenis-gamer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Main game sekarang nggak cuma sekedar main aja. Sumber: Video Game History</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Para Conventional Gamer bagaikan satwa langka di masa kini. Dahulu, mereka adalah jenis gamer yang duduk di tengah-tengah posisi kasual dan hardcore. Namun seiring berkembangnya zaman dan semakin banyaknya aktivitas yang berhubungan dengan game, para Conventional Gamer ini kembali pecah menjadi klasifikasi di atas. Yang mereka lakukan sekarang hanyalah bermain game sendirian dan sesekali menonton orang lain bermain.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Itu dia delapan jenis gamer masa kini menurut survei dari Newzoo. Gamer yang manakah kamu, diantara delapan tipe di atas? Jika kamu bingung, kamu bisa mencoba survei tersebut <a href=\"https://newzoo.com/insights/quizzes/what-type-of-game-enthusiast-are-you/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">di sini</a>. Jika sudah, jangan sungkan untuk membagikan hasilnya di kolom komentar!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"5798c909-f45f-5e0c-8e2c-09f50fa15643"}}}